---
// FounderCredibility.astro
---

<section class="section founder-section">
   <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="founder-grid">
         <div class="founder-image reveal delay-1">
            <div class="image-frame">
               <img src="/founder-tavares.webp" alt="Tavares - Founder da Hausly" class="founder-img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="500" />
               <div class="founder-overlay"></div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="founder-content reveal delay-2">
            <h2 class="h-section">O mercado mudou. A gestão também precisa mudar.</h2>
            <div class="quote-box">
               <span class="quote-mark">"</span>
               <p class="t-lead">
                  Como engenheiro de software e investidor do mercado imobiliário, percebi o quanto os corretores perdiam dinheiro simplesmente pela falta de gestão. A Hausly nasceu para aplicar tecnologia de ponta na dor mais básica da rua: não esquecer de ninguém.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-author">
               <strong>Guilherme Tavares</strong>
               <span>Engenheiro de Software & Founder</span>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>

<style>
   .founder-section {
      padding: 96px 0;
      position: relative;
   }

   .founder-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
   }

   .founder-image {
      position: relative;
   }

   .image-frame {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
   }

   .founder-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: grayscale(30%) contrast(1.2);
   }

   .founder-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--bg-deep) 0%, transparent 40%);
   }

   .quote-box {
      margin: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
      position: relative;
   }

   .quote-mark {
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px;
      left: -20px;
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 6rem;
      color: var(--amber);
      opacity: 0.2;
      line-height: 1;
   }

   .founder-content .t-lead {
      color: var(--text-pure);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
   }

   .founder-author {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
   }

   .founder-author strong {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--amber);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
   }

   .founder-author span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-weight: 500;
   }

   @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .founder-grid {
         grid-template-columns: 1fr;
         text-align: center;
         gap: var(--space-xl);
      }
      
      .image-frame {
         max-width: 300px;
         margin: 0 auto;
         aspect-ratio: 1/1;
         border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      }

      .quote-mark {
         left: 50%;
         transform: translateX(-50%);
         top: -30px;
      }
   }
</style>
